    "title": {
      "rendered": "3 Mobile Compatible Nonprofit e-Newsletters to Subscribe To and Learn From"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/mobile-email-for-nonprofits.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-15559\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"mobile email for nonprofits\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/mobile-email-for-nonprofits-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/mobile-email-for-nonprofits.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/mobile-email-for-nonprofits.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/mobile-email-for-nonprofits.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/mobile-email-for-nonprofits.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/mobile-email-for-nonprofits.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>With <a href=\"https://litmus.com/blog/email-client-market-share-where-people-opened-in-2013\">51% of email</a> now being opened on a tablet or smartphone, nonprofits would be wise to redesign their e-newsletter as soon as possible. Long-standing e-newsletter design best practices such as a two or three-column-fixed layout, 12 point font size, and text-based links only are officially 51% less effective. Unless your nonprofit embraces\u00a0<a href=\"http://zurb.com/playground/responsive-email-templates\">responsive design</a> or mobile-first design aesthetics, your stories and calls-to-action will go unread and untapped. If email is \u00a0integral to your communications and fundraising strategy, redesigning your e-newsletter to make it mobile compatible should be at the top of your to do list.</p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">1. Water.org: Mobile-First Design</h2>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Not responsive, one narrow column, large photos and font,<br />\nand large, colorful, tappable call-to-action buttons.</h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://water.org/help/?utm_source=water_org&amp;utm_medium=web&amp;utm_campaign=button_header&amp;utm_content=get_involved\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15532\" alt=\"orange subscribe\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/orange-subscribe1.png?resize=125%2C40\" width=\"125\" height=\"40\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/water.org-e-newsletter.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-15527\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"water.org e-newsletter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/water.org-e-newsletter.png?resize=600%2C337\" width=\"600\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/water.org-e-newsletter.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/water.org-e-newsletter.png?resize=300%2C168&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/water.org-e-newsletter-2.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-15528\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"water.org e-newsletter 2\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/water.org-e-newsletter-2.png?resize=600%2C337\" width=\"600\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/water.org-e-newsletter-2.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/water.org-e-newsletter-2.png?resize=300%2C168&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<table width=\"600\" border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/water1.png?resize=195%2C293\" width=\"195\" height=\"293\" border=\"1\" /></td>\n<td align=\"center\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/water2.png?resize=195%2C293\" width=\"195\" height=\"293\" border=\"1\" /></td>\n<td align=\"center\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/water3.png?resize=195%2C293\" width=\"195\" height=\"293\" border=\"1\" /></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">2. Wildlife Alliance: One-Column Responsive Design</h2>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Simple, large banner, large font, and large tappable &#8220;Donate&#8221; button.</h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.wildlifealliance.org/page/view/305/newsletter\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15532\" alt=\"orange subscribe\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/orange-subscribe1.png?resize=125%2C40\" width=\"125\" height=\"40\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/wildlife-alliance-e-newsletter-1.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-15535\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"wildlife alliance e-newsletter 1\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/wildlife-alliance-e-newsletter-1.png?resize=600%2C337\" width=\"600\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/wildlife-alliance-e-newsletter-1.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/wildlife-alliance-e-newsletter-1.png?resize=300%2C168&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/wildlife-alliance-e-newsletter-2.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-15536\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"wildlife alliance e-newsletter 2\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/wildlife-alliance-e-newsletter-2.png?resize=600%2C337\" width=\"600\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/wildlife-alliance-e-newsletter-2.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/wildlife-alliance-e-newsletter-2.png?resize=300%2C168&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<table width=\"600\" border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/wildlife-alliance-e-newsletter-11.png?resize=195%2C293\" width=\"195\" height=\"293\" /></td>\n<td align=\"center\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/wildlife-alliance-e-newsletter-21.png?resize=195%2C293\" width=\"195\" height=\"293\" /></td>\n<td align=\"center\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/wildlife-alliance-e-newsletter-3.png?resize=195%2C293\" width=\"195\" height=\"293\" /></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">3. Mercy Corps: Two-Column Responsive Design</h2>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Large headline, minimal text, visuals prioritized, and large tappable<br />\ncall-to-action buttons.</h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.mercycorps.org/signup\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-15532\" alt=\"orange subscribe\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/orange-subscribe1.png?resize=125%2C40\" width=\"125\" height=\"40\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/mercy-corps-1.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-15542\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"mercy corps 1\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/mercy-corps-1.png?resize=600%2C337\" width=\"600\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/mercy-corps-1.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/mercy-corps-1.png?resize=300%2C168&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/mercy-corps-2.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-15543\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"mercy corps 2\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/mercy-corps-2.png?resize=600%2C337\" width=\"600\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/mercy-corps-2.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/mercy-corps-2.png?resize=300%2C168&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<table width=\"600\" border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/mercy-corps-enewsletter-1.png?resize=195%2C293\" width=\"195\" height=\"293\" /></td>\n<td align=\"center\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/mercy-corps-newsletter-2.png?resize=195%2C293\" width=\"195\" height=\"293\" /></td>\n<td align=\"center\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/mercy-corps-newsletter-3.png?resize=195%2C293\" width=\"195\" height=\"293\" /></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n",
